@DATABASE "Cybernoid 2"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - C - Cybernoid 2"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - C
                   ====================================

                                Cybernoid 2
                                ===========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(36059,0)"}       36059,0
@{"Infinite Shields " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(30529,0)"}       30529,0
@{"Immunity         " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35911,201)"}       35911,201
@{"No Guns          " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35504,201)"}       35504,201
@{"No Lifts         " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33216,201)"}       33216,201
@{"No Snake         " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(36699,201)"}       36699,201
@{"No Rockets       " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38441,201)"}       38441,201
@{"No Flying Aliens " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38677,201)"}       38677,201
@{"No Passage Aliens" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33725,201)"}       33725,201
@{"Game Speed = x   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33725,0)"}       33725,x (x= 0-255)

                         For the "Game Speed" POKE the normal speed is 175.
                         You can try messing about with different speeds,
                         but I think there are only about 3 real speeds.
                         Watch out though. Sometimes, I crashed the game
                         if I changed the speed while playing!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
